Name: Rectangular Rock Block
Desc: Tubby combined Paimon's description of your adventures in Simulanka with her own imagination to create this greenery-draped rock.\nThe extremely regular shape of this massive boulder is like a ginormous toy block that could be freely assembled and rearranged. However, anyone wishing to move such a sturdy stone would need a ginormous amount of strength. Only the strongest — and those using cranes — could play them with like toy blocks...
